<div class="section-container problem-content">
  <span class="section-label">The problem we're solving</span>

  <h2 class="problem-title">
    Nepal needs data-ready <span class="accent">climate professionals</span>. Now.
  </h2>

  <p class="problem-description">
    Climate change, floods, biodiversity loss, air pollution - these crises are intensifying. Yet many environmental graduates lack the data and analytical skills to spot trends or drive evidence-based decisions. The NCH Data Fellowship closes that gap.
  </p>

  <div class="quote-box">
    <p class="quote-text">
      <q>Many graduates have strong conceptual knowledge but lack the practical, technical competencies required to solve real-world environmental problems. This leaves them underprepared for research, policy, and climate action in an increasingly data-driven world.</q>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="doughnut"></div>
</div>

<style>
  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 12px;
    color: #CEFE00;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .problem-title {
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-family: "Zilla Slab", serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 50px;
    color: white;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .problem-title .accent {
    color: #CEFE00;
  }

  .problem-description {
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 29px;
    color: #F8F9FA;
    max-width: 840px;
  }

  .quote-box {
    margin-top: 40px;
    border-left: 3px solid #CEFE00;
    background-color: rgba(206, 254, 0, 0.05);
    padding: 24px;
    border-top-right-radius: 4px;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
    max-width: 973px;
    padding-right: 200px;
  }

  .quote-text {
    font-family: "Zilla Slab", serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 29px;
    color: white;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .doughnut {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    transform: translate(35%, -30%);
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    border: 80px solid #969393;
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  
  @media screen and (max-width: 1200px) {
    .doughnut {
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      border-width: 60px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
    .problem-title { font-size: 36px; line-height: 40px; }
    .problem-description { font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px; }
    .quote-text { font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px; }
    .doughnut {
      width: 250px;
      height: 250px;
      border-width: 50px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .problem-title { font-size: 30px; line-height: 32px; }
    .problem-description { font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; }
    .quote-box { padding: 20px; }
    .quote-text { font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; }
    .doughnut {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      border-width: 40px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
    .problem-title { font-size: 24px; line-height: 28px; }
    .doughnut {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      border-width: 30px;
    }
  }
</style>
